# 1Password reference file. Safe to commit — holds only 1Password references.
# `op inject -i .env.op > .env` runs automatically on `mise` directory enter,
# materializing real values into .env (gitignored). Rotated secrets propagate
# on the next enter, so never hand-edit .env.
#
# Reference format: op :// <vault> / <item> / <field>  (without the spaces).

# ── Plane (33god workspace) ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# Read/write this repo's ONE ticket board (identifier SIDE) — consumed by the
# Hermes PM + Scrum Master agents and, eventually, the Sidepiece sidebar itself.
# The 33god key is the `apiKey` field of the DeLoSecrets item titled "Plane".
# (The former duplicate was renamed to "Plane (AutomaticAI / HelloSubconscious)",
# so this title now resolves unambiguously.)
PLANE_33GOD_API_KEY=op://DeLoSecrets/Plane/apiKey
PLANE_API_KEY=op://DeLoSecrets/Plane/apiKey
PLANE_BASE_URL=https://plane.delo.sh
PLANE_WORKSPACE=33god

# ── LLM inference ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
OPENROUTER_API_KEY=op://DeLoSecrets/openrouter/OpenCode
